title: Justice Cunningham earns historic preservation award
content: Justice Bill Cunningham receives the Ida Lee Willis Memorial Award silver cup from foundation board members during the 39th annual Ida Lee Willis Memorial Foundation Historic Preservation Awards at the Governor's Mansion in Frankfort.
